{"tid":2061970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跟我講，係「情操高尚」鼓吹「持刀斬人」","createTime":"2020-06-12T19:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T07:51:42.000Z","uid":101507,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"4c3c4bc1ffbbfcb4b74f2a0ff0154c1f3ba2e114","tid":2061970,"uid":101507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T19:20:03.000Z","msg":"大家仲未消除對郭偉健既怒氣，今晚已經發生另一宗持刀斬人案<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好難唔令人覺得條友係受「情操高尚」既影響<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下提供本人草稿既投訴內容<br />\n歡迎各位自取及修改<br />\n假若文筆欠佳，還請大家原諒<br />\n<br />\n投訴裁判官只限書面形式<br />\n大家需要print出黎寄出去<br />\n<br />\n投訴信格式 傳送門：<a href=\"https://www.judiciary.hk/zh/court_services_facilities/complaintsjjo.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.judiciary.hk%2Fzh%2Fcourt_services_facilities%2Fcomplaintsjjo.html&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=126830e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.judiciary.hk/zh/court_services_facilities/complaintsjjo.html</a><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n甲部\t填寫個人資料<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乙部<br />\n法官姓名：郭偉健<br />\n法院名稱：區域法院<br />\n聆訊日期：24/4/2020<br />\n案件編號：DCCC834/2019<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本人現投訴區域法院法官郭偉健於審理案件（DCCC834/2019）時違反立場中肯的原則，促使他人模仿犯罪，導致社會進一步撕裂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳「連儂隧道」斬人案的受傷記者臉部、胸部均有傷口，更有一根肋骨骨折，出現中度氣胸及血胸。其後更確診創傷後壓力症，身心受創。裁判官郭偉健在審理該案時，卻於判詞中以「情操高尚」形容斬人者，不單是因政見而作出的不當言論，更是對受害人所造成的二次傷害，令人髮指。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然而，在2020年6月12日晚上於觀塘發生了另一宗因政見問題而持刀傷人的案件。當晚，民建聯前社區主任鄺星宇企圖用生果刀襲擊記者，並刺傷了阻止他的市民。其後，更被網民揭發他在事前已於社交網站張貼犯罪宣言。由此可見，郭位健法官的不當言論已促使他人照板煮碗，以為「持刀斬人」的行為是會得到社會認可的高尚行為，導致社會進一步撕裂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n綜合上述，本人認為裁判官郭偉健無法秉持法官立場中立的原則，更犯下無可挽救的過失，鼓吹暴力，導致社會進一步撕裂，質疑他是否應該繼續擔任裁判官一職。"},{"pid":"dd82354c8dcf8740edd42d091efa990bd919b09a","tid":2061970,"uid":101507,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T19:21:41.000Z","msg":"幫推另一位手足寫既投訴信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[內附懶人包] 一鍵投訴紅官吳重儀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6f556960b1e015abdf27f1d8808e14525024120b","tid":2061970,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T19:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32eb30fd108150930e696e190b8dea0b7a55d753","tid":2061970,"uid":101507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T19:22:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abe0b3453d49ecc05c790ba1325b6341ebe657ce","tid":2061970,"uid":101507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T19:25:40.000Z","msg":"狙擊紅底官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e07ac2d3677acc4b12cabe597d0aa52f4f0f174","tid":2061970,"uid":299276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T19:26:44.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e956b7f5db7496bb213e23fddfd3f18c55b834dc","tid":2061970,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd82354c8dcf8740edd42d091efa990bd919b09a","tid":2061970,"uid":101507,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T19:21:41.000Z","msg":"幫推另一位手足寫既投訴信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[內附懶人包] 一鍵投訴紅官吳重儀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T19:26:52.000Z","msg":"做乜加密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90573592e38c1e2a2330aeaddd433b51d591966e","tid":2061970,"uid":101507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e956b7f5db7496bb213e23fddfd3f18c55b834dc","tid":2061970,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd82354c8dcf8740edd42d091efa990bd919b09a","tid":2061970,"uid":101507,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T19: